Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
set_power_output_dir(25.10)                        set_power_output_dir(25.10)

Name
       set_power_output_dir  -  Specifies the name of the directory that power
       information will be output to

Syntax
       set_power_output_dir <dir>

       [-reset]

       Specifies the name of the directory that power information will be out-
       put to.

Parameters
       <dir>  Specifies the name of the directory in which power analysis out-
              put information is written.

       -reset Resets all options back to default values.

Examples
              * The following command specifies the  output  directory  called
                static_power_AvallOn  in  which the power information is writ-
                ten.

                set_power_output_dir static_power_AVallOn

Related Information
              * set_power_analysis_mode

              * "Static Power, IRdrop and EM Analysis" in the Voltus IC  Power
                Integrity Solution User Guide

              * "Dynamic Power and IRDrop Analysis" in the Voltus IC Power In-
                tegrity Solution User Guide

